graycsflh.Description: contrast-to-noise ratio of gray matter and CSF in left hemisphere

graycsfrh.Description: contrast-to-noise ratio of gray matter and CSF in right hemisphere

graywhitelh.Description: contrast-to-noise ratio of gray matter and white matter in left hemisphere

graywhiterh.Description: contrast-to-noise ratio of gray matter and white matter in right hemisphere

left_holes.Description: the number of holes in left hemisphere

right_holes.Description: the number of holes in right hemisphere

left_total_defect_index.Description: total defect index based on euler and holes in left hemisphere

right_total_defect_index.Description: total defect index based on euler and holes in right hemisphere

graycsf_flag.Description: exclusion flag based on CNR in gray matter and CSF

graywhite_flag.Description: exclusion flag based on CNR in gray and white matter
